title: Huge 1200sq ft (2) Bedroom Apartment DELEADED
posting_body: ['**Very nice Sun Drenched oversized 1,200 Sq Ft', '**2 bedroom apartment on 1st floor.', 'Deleaded Unit', '**Tall Ceilings make apt feel extra spacious', '** Newer Granite kitchen Fully applianced with Dishwasher, Stove, Frigerator.', ' Features Lovely open floor plan into living room/ formal dining room.', '2 generous sized Bedrooms w/Hardwood Flooring', 'Formal dining room (ceiling fan)', 'Living Room (ceiling fan)', 'Private In Unit Laundry hook up (bring your machines/photo with checkered floor).', 'Bathroom has a full tub, tile floor, granite counter.', 'Unit has high efficiency water heater & heating system, also the home has blown in insulation.', '2 Designated off street parking spots.', 'Close to train about 3/4 mile, Town park and center of town is a stones throw away.', '$2225.00 a month plus utilities.', 'Will need first/last/security totaling $6675 to move in.', 'Tenant responsible for gas, electric, and cable.', 'Owner pays for water, sewer, and trash pickup.', 'Will do credit/Cori checks.', 'The perfect applicants would be quiet and courtesy in order fit in with the existing 2 amazing tenants.', 'No SMOKING On premises.', ' Pets Considered.', 'Unit Available October 15th', 'PLEASE EMAIL me a personalized note so that i know you are not a Bot and your phone number if you wish for me to call you directly.']
